  "intent_precise": "Library Prep Clean Up: Using Reservoir (reservoir, slot 1), magplate (pcr_plate, slot Mag Plate), 96-well plate (pcr_plate, slot 2), 384-well plate (plate, slot 3). With magnetic module. (1) Mix 5 times at 30\u00b5L. (2) Transfer 15\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (3) Mix 10 times at 40\u00b5L. (4) Incubate for 5 minutes. (5) Engage magnets for bead separation. (6) Incubate for 2 minutes. (7) Distribute 200\u00b5L from source A1 to destination wells A1, A1, A1. (8) Wait 30 seconds. (9) Transfer 200\u00b5L from source (A1, A1) to destination (A1, A1). (10) Incubate for 15 minutes. (11) Disengage magnets to release beads. (12) Transfer 25\u00b5L from source A1 to destination A1. (13) Mix 10 times at 25\u00b5L. (14) Incubate for 2 minutes. (15) Engage magnets for bead separation. (16) Incubate for 2 minutes. (17) Transfer 24\u00b5L from source to destination.",
  "intent_concise": "Perform distribute to A1, A1, A1, magnetic bead separation. (volumes 4\u00b5L-200\u00b5L, ~28 min total)",
  "intent": "For this library prep cleanup, you'll be working with the reservoir in slot 1, the magnetic plate, the 96-well plate in slot 2, and the 384-well plate in slot 3. Start by mixing 5 times at 30\u00b5L, then transfer 15\u00b5L from A1 to A1 and mix 10 times at 40\u00b5L before incubating for 5 minutes. Engage the magnets for bead separation, wait 2 minutes, then distribute 200\u00b5L from A1 to three A1 wells, wait 30 seconds, and transfer 200\u00b5L between the A1 positions before a 15-minute incubation. Finally, disengage the magnets, transfer 25\u00b5L from A1 to A1, mix 10 times at 25\u00b5L, incubate for 2 minutes, re-engage magnets for another 2 minutes, and finish with a 24\u00b5L transfer from source to destination.",
